*Sestre su stalno u kontaktu preko telefona (The sisters are always in contact via phone). 

One su često zajedno uživale u izletima* (They often enjoyed trips together). 

Učenje je bilo uživanje za *sestre* (Learning was a pleasure for the sisters). 

Njihove *sestre* su živele u drugim gradovima (Their sisters lived in other cities).

Nakon škole, *sestre* su se često družile (After school, the sisters often hung out together). 

*Sestre* su se stalno međusobno podržavale (The sisters always supported each other).